API of this class could be cleaner.  Currently its exposing implementation detail on its API, i.e. it's extending VisitParentExpressionVisitor.
Better / cleaner to instead have the visitor as an internal implementation detail and clean, documented, API for this class:
class GenericExpressionResolver {

  .... 

   public Object resolve(final Expression expression) {
      return new Visitor().process(expression, null);
   }

   private static class Visitor extends VisitParentExpressionVisitor<Object, Void> {
      ...
   }
}

